title: Saint Laurent Medium Kate Shoulder Bag
description: Saint Laurent medium Kate shoulder bag in black grainy leather. Featuring gold-toned hardware, single sliding chain shoulder strap and gold 'YSL' logo plaque at front. The magnetic snap closure on flap opens to a black textile interior with a patch pocket. Approximate dimensions: 24cm(L) x 15.5cm(H) x 5.5cm(D), and single chain drop 49cm. Accompanied by YSL dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
